@startuml SignalCaptureAI_EndToEnd_Sequence
title SignalCaptureAI - End-to-End Flow (Onboarding to Lead Capture)
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
skinparam BoxPadding 10

legend top right
  **Risk Levels (Transactions & Actor Swimlanes)**
  |<#White> Black Arrow | Internal / Low Risk Operation |
  |<#F2F9FF> Light Blue Box | Trusted Internal System Boundary |
  |<#Orange> Orange Arrow | PII Processing / IAM Auth (Medium Risk) |
  |<#FFE6CC> Light Orange Box| Edge Transit / 3rd Party (Medium Risk) |
  |<#Red> Red Arrow | External PII Ingress-Egress (High Risk) |
  |<#FFCCCC> Light Red Box| Untrusted External Actors (High Risk) |
endlegend

box "Internal Operations" #E6F2FF
actor "Sales / CRM" as CRM
actor "Finance" as Finance
end box

box "Trusted Cloud Hub (Low Risk Env)" #F2F9FF
participant "CI/CD Pipeline" as Pipeline
participant "Terraform (IaC)" as TF
participant "Azure Infrastructure\n& Keyfactor (PKI)" as Azure
participant "Azure App (Docker)" as Docker
participant "Tenant SQL DB" as DB
participant "AI Engine\n(Whisper / OCR)" as AI
end box

box "Edge Transit & IAM (Med Risk)" #FFE6CC
participant "Cloudflare" as CF
participant "Identity Provider\n(WorkOS SSO)" as IDP
end box

box "External Actors (High Risk)" #FFCCCC
actor "Client Tenant Admin" as Admin
actor "Sales Rep (Event)" as Rep
actor "Lead" as Lead
end box

== 1. Sales & Financial Approval ==
CRM -> Finance: Sale Completed (Request Order Approval)
activate Finance
Finance -> Pipeline: Approves Order & Triggers Provisioning
deactivate Finance

== 2. Automated Infrastructure Provisioning ==
activate Pipeline
Pipeline -> TF: Execute Terraform Plan/Apply for New Tenant
activate TF
TF -> Azure: Provision isolated SQL Database
TF -> Azure: Request Keyfactor PKI for DB Encryption
Azure --> TF: DB provisioned & encrypted
TF -[#orange]-> IDP: Configure Tenant Auth (WorkOS Organisation)
IDP --[#orange]-> TF: Auth configured
TF --> Pipeline: Provisioning Complete
deactivate TF
Pipeline -> CRM: Client Created & Infrastructure Ready
deactivate Pipeline

== 3. Client Tenant Event Setup ==
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: Login to Platform
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: Upload Product Documentation
Docker -> DB: Store Docs in Tenant DB
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: Create New Tracking Event

== 4. Lead Capture Workflow (Geo-Routed) ==
Rep -[#orange]-> IDP: Login securely
IDP --[#orange]-> Rep: Auth Token
Rep -> Docker: Select Event
Rep -[#red]-> Rep: Scan Business Card (OCR)\n& Record Voice Note
Rep -[#red]-> CF: Submit Lead Data (Photo + Audio)
activate CF
CF -> CF: Evaluate Geo-Headers

alt Strict Localization Not Required (Default to EU)
    CF -[#orange]-> Docker: Route to EU Privacy Hub
else Strict Sovereign Local Laws Apply
    CF -[#orange]-> Docker: Route to Regional Spoke
end
deactivate CF

activate Docker
Docker -[#orange]-> AI: Pass Audio & OCR Data
activate AI
AI --[#orange]-> Docker: Extracted Text & Voice Transcript
Docker -> DB: Fetch Product Docs for Cross-Reference
DB --> Docker: Product Docs
Docker -[#orange]-> AI: Analyze Transcript vs Product Docs
AI --[#orange]-> Docker: Generated Draft Message
deactivate AI

Docker -[#orange]-> DB: Store Lead PII & Draft (Encrypted)
Docker --[#orange]-> Rep: Present Draft Message for Review
deactivate Docker

== 5. Human-in-the-Loop & Delivery ==
Rep -[#orange]-> Docker: Review & Approve Draft
Docker -[#red]-> Lead: Dispatch via Email / WhatsApp

== 6. Compliance / Admin ==
Admin -[#orange]-> Docker: View Tenant Meta-Metrics
Admin -[#red]-> DB: Query/Delete Subject Data (upon request)
@enduml
